embeds.description:
**🏅 1:  @ps - Times on Starboard: 20**
🥈 2:  @lo - Times on Starboard: 18

🎖 9:  @UserOwO - Times on Starboard: 5
🎖 10:  @Dagoth Theodore - Times on Starboard: 4

Myself:
what a time. what a fucking time it's been in four years. four years ago, today, i was in the middle of summer break-- as i am now, of course-- some random child who was gonna start running Cross Country soon, and had only just started becoming aware of the world, and became a bit of a mirror image of my parents in terms of politics
the point is-- i've changed, a lot.
and for that, without a shadow of doubt, i have every last one of you to thank
there is no word i can use to do justice the effect you guys have had, and continue to have, on my life. every last inside joke, every last shitpost, it all means so fucking much to me and i smile at the thought of this server because it is INTEGRAL to who i am today. once upon a time i sat awkwardly in the corner as everyone was in botrp and "actual-general" was quiet

once upon a time this server got less than 400 messages a day and truth be told it felt so close to being done and in that time i felt genuinely hollow
once upon a time we sat and planned and coordinated and suddenly was born a minecraft server

once upon a time we lost our shit at how easy it was to fuck with Clyde

and each of these experiences have molded me into who i am today

i want you guys to all understand what you mean to me
i want you guys to all understand that i care
for this server
for you, individually
for each and every one of you
i dont care what you think of yourself
if your humour is passive or self-deprecating
i care about you
if you needed help id be there
because each of you are all worth something to me in your own little ways and when all these little things connect together this is what we get
this beautiful corner of the internet that ive genuinely never seen anywhere else
this place is something special
and i hope ive had at least half as much of an effect on you as you have on me

keep being yourself, cause i dunno where i'd be if you didn't

-Spray :)

heres to another 100,000 messages, heres to another 4 years
